extensionMeta.name: Sheet Navigation & Actions
extensionMeta.description: Sense Sheet Navigation + Actions visualization extension for Qlik Sense.
extensionMeta.author: Stefan Walther

qDef.qDef:
Pick
(
    [%SynHeadersSix_EMC]
    ,
	(
    	Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
    	+
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
    )
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month1)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month2)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month3)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month4)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month5)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_MT_Month6)

    
)

Pick
(
    [%SynHeadersSix_EMC]
    ,
	(
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
          +
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
    )
    
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month1)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month2)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month3)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month4)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month5)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month6)

)/1000

Pick
(
    [%SynHeadersSix_EMC]
    ,
    
    (
      (
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
          +
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
      )
      /
      (
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
          +
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
      )
    )
    
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month1_Per_MT)
	,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month2_Per_MT)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month3_Per_MT)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month4_Per_MT)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month5_Per_MT)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Amount_Month6_Per_MT)

   
)

Pick
(
    [%SynHeadersSix_EMC]
    ,
    
    (
      (
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
          +
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
      )
      /
      (
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
          +
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])
      )
    )
    
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Cost_Amount_Month1_Per_MT)
	,$(v_Backlog_Order_Cost_Amount_Month2_Per_MT)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Cost_Amount_Month3_Per_MT)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Cost_Amount_Month4_Per_MT)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Cost_Amount_Month5_Per_MT)
    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Cost_Amount_Month6_Per_MT)


)

Pick
(
    [%SynHeadersSix_EMC]
    ,
    
    (
      (
      	(
          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])

          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])

          Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Backlog'},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Backlog Order MT])

    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Contribution_Amount_Month1_Per_MT)

    ,$(v_Backlog_Order_Contribution_Amount_Month3_Per_MT)
